lup)</a>于<a href="https://graph.facebook.com/100060537856765/posts/1062854685742450/">2024 年 9 月 9 日星期一</a></p></blockquote></div><p>这一消息是在<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-cure-releas-two-brand-new-songs-as-live-recordings-double-a-side-for-climate-charity-3788702">乐队的两首新歌现场录制发行之前发布的，这首歌曲将成为气候慈善机构“Earth Percent”的双 A 面歌曲</a>。</p><p>通过<a href="https://nakedrecordclub.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Naked Record Club</a> （一家发行可持续黑胶限量版唱片的唱片公司）发行的《The Cure – Novembre：Live in France 2022》是一首双 A-Side 12 英寸生态黑胶单曲，包含两首在可持续黑胶唱片上录制的现场曲目。<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/the-cure-wembley-arena-review-photos-setlist-3365275">乐队“Shows Of A Lost World”巡演的</a>法国站。</p><p>第一首歌曲“And Nothing Is Forever”于 2022 年 11 月 8 日在蒙彼利埃的法国南部竞技场现场录制，而“I Can Never Say Goodbye”则于 2022 年 11 月 13 日在图卢兹 Zénith 现场录制。 The Cure 16 年来首张新曲目。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/Cl4fTVAKM9u/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xli