'Open Sans', 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif;" href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/danny-masterson-sentenced-to-30-years-to-life-in-prison-for-rape-3494826">定罪的强奸犯丹尼·马斯特森</a>有联系之后，很快就引起了争议。这是在<a style="font-family: Verdana, BlinkMacSystemFont, -apple-system, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, 'Open Sans', 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif;" href="https://www.nme.com/artists/at-the-drive-in">火星</a><a style="font-family: Verdana, BlinkMacSystemFont, -apple-system, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, 'Open Sans', 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif;" href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-mars-volta">沃尔塔（Mars Volta）</a>发送给阿姆斯特朗（Armstrong）的一条消息后，而前任前任<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/linkin-park-fans-re-share-cedric-bixler-zavalas-message-to-emily-armstrong-over-alleged-links-to-scientology-and-danny-masterson-3791311">塞德里克·比克斯勒·扎瓦拉（Cedric Bixler-Zavala）在周末再循环的</a>一条消息后，这一发现了。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/cedric-bixler-zavala-shares-meme-around-linkin-park-emily-armstrong-controversy-i-fucking-told-you-3791596">在周末，在Bixler-Zavala分享的另一篇文章</a>中，他写道：“我他妈的告诉你。” </p><figure id="attachment_3791947" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3791947" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3791947" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Linkin-Park@2000x1270-1.jpg" alt="Linkin Park的Emily Armstrong和Mike Shinoda于2024年9月演出" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Linkin-Park@2000x1270-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Linkin-Park@2000x1270-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Linkin-Park@2000x1270-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Linkin-Park@2000x1270-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Linkin-Park@2000x1270-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Linkin-Park@2000x1270-1-1068x678.jpg