-n-Shinoda-Screenshot1@2000-1068x1941.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 1600px) 100vw, 1600px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3791936" class="wp-caption-text"> Jaime Bennington Instagram故事屏幕截图。学分： @thepicturepiecesharchive/instagram</figcaption></figure><p> “嘿，迈克！人们并不艰难地将自己的头脑缠绕着Linkin Park重塑本身的前景。” Bennington写道。 “他们很难围绕您的方式缠着自己的头脑：雇用了很多年的朋友@emilyarmstrong取代@Chesterbe知道艾米丽在教堂中的历史，以及她作为@dannymasterson的盟友的历史。”</p><p>他继续指责Shinoda“在国际自杀预防月期间实时静静地抹去了我父亲的生活和遗产”，并“拒绝承认雇用像艾米丽这样的人的影响，没有太多的影响关于组成您核心粉丝群的各种受害者的澄清声明。” </p><figure id="attachment_3791937" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3791937" style="width: 1600px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3791937" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Benningt-n-Shinoda-Screenshot2@2000.jpg" alt="" width="1600" height="2861" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Benningt-n-Shinoda-Screenshot2@2000.jpg 1600w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Benningt-n-Shinoda-Screenshot2@2000-400x715.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Benningt-n-Shinoda-Screenshot2@2000-800x1431.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Benningt-n-Shinoda-Screenshot2@2000-696x1245.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Benningt-n-Shinoda-Screenshot2@2000-1392x2489.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Benningt-n-Shinoda-Screenshot2@2000-1068x1910.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 1600px) 100vw, 1600px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3791937" class="wp-caption-text"> Jaime Bennington Instagram故事屏幕截图。学分： @thepicturepiecesharchive/instagram </figcaption></figure><figure id="attachment_3791938" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3791938" style="width: 1600px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3791938" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Benningt-n-Shinoda-Screenshot3@2000.jpg" alt="" width="1600" height="2877" srcs